column3: Home|Supplies & Equipment|Tape and Tape Dispensers
column4:
Definite Length Tape Dispenser

The Tach-It Model #5000 definite length tape dispenser is perfect for applications where a fixed 1½ inch length of tape is needed. Usable with 1½ wide roll or 2 individual 3/4 inch wide rolls, by simply turning the large knob the model 5000 applies the tape to a star wheel for easy removal. Perfect for gift wrap, retail, and industrial applications where a 1½ inch piece of tape is required, the Model #5000 also has a separate free mandrel for 3/4 inch tape with unlimited lengths.

column1:
Color Tissue Paper Roll
20" x 5000' Color Tissue Paper on Roll
column3: Home|Tissue Paper|Color Tissue Paper Rolls - Made in USA
column4:
Color tissue paper counter rolls.
20" x 5,000' color tissue paper counter rolls.
Tissue Bases Weight: 10# (17gsm)
SatinWrap Tissue Paper colors.  These colors are an exact match to the sheeted tissue papers we stock.  The only difference is that this is in roll form.
The main benefit of tissue paper on a roll are you can tear off as much or little tissue paper as you need which means there is zero waste compared to sheet tissue paper.
Custom printing and custom colors are available for as little as 16 rolls.  Contact customerservice@packagingsource.com for MOQ, pricing and lead times.
Made in USA.
Paper cutters are available.  We recommend ordering the 24" paper cutter to hold the 20" tissue paper rolls.
